title: Most sectors will continue to advance this year, says Wells Fargo Asset Management's Margie Patel
text:
Most sectors will continue to advance this year, says Wells Fargo Asset Management's Margie Patel Thursday, February 22, 2018 - 03:08 
We're on course to get three more quarter point rate increases, with the qualification that the Fed is very sensitive to the financial markets, says Margie Patel, senior portfolio manager at Wells Fargo Asset Management. Aleksandra Michalska reports.
